<title>USA: TABLE - Tecnomatix Q2 net increases.</title>
<headline>TABLE - Tecnomatix Q2 net increases.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-07-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months ended	 Three months ended</p>
<p>		     06/30/97    06/30/96     06/30/97   06/30/96</p>
<p>Total revenues     26,216     20,151	13,894     10,573</p>
<p>Net income	    4,987	2,866	 2,898	1,794</p>
<p>Earning per share    0.47	 0.32	  0.27	 0.19</p>
<p>Weighted average number of shares outstanding</p>
<p>		   10,632,083  9,033,502  10,743,725  9,539,993</p>
<p>(U.S $ in thousands, except per share data)</p>
<p>NOTE:  Tecnomatix Technologies Ltd said its per share results were affected by an increase in the weighted average number of shares outstanding due to the company's follow-on public offering of 1,637,980 ordinary shares completed in May 1996.</p>
